name: Lugano Wall Mounted Cabinet
description: Looking sleek, elegant and exclusive, Lugano will solve all your storage needs without breaking a sweat. Lugano media units come with cut outs for cables. The cut out also ensures ventilation for your electronics. Front options in different materials allow you to customise your solution to match your existing interior. The design is completed with bevelled edges, ensuring harmony and bringing an elegance and exclusivity to the expression.
